---
import DocsLayout from '../../../layouts/DocsLayout.astro';
import Aside from '../../../components/Aside.astro';
import {funktorSidebar} from '../../../data/funktor-sidebar';
import {Code} from 'astro:components';
---

<DocsLayout title="Insights Module" sidebar={funktorSidebar} description="Request profiling and performance monitoring">

    <h1>Insights</h1>

    <p class="text-xl text-gray-400 !mt-2 !mb-8">
        Request profiling, performance metrics, and a built-in debug GUI.
    </p>

    <h2>What it collects</h2>

    <p>Insights uses per-request <a href="/ultra/kontainer/">Kontainer</a> scoping to collect data throughout
        a request's lifecycle. Each collector gathers one kind of data:</p>

    <div class="not-prose grid grid-cols-1 sm:grid-cols-2 gap-4 my-8">
        <div class="p-4 rounded-xl border border-white/10 bg-white/[0.02]">
            <h3 class="text-white font-semibold mb-1">RequestCollector</h3>
            <p class="text-sm text-gray-400">HTTP method, URI, headers, query parameters.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="p-4 rounded-xl border border-white/10 bg-white/[0.02]">
            <h3 class="text-white font-semibold mb-1">ResponseCollector</h3>
            <p class="text-sm text-gray-400">Status code, response time, content type.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="p-4 rounded-xl border border-white/10 bg-white/[0.02]">
            <h3 class="text-white font-semibold mb-1">VaultCollector</h3>
            <p class="text-sm text-gray-400">Database queries executed, query times, results.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="p-4 rounded-xl border border-white/10 bg-white/[0.02]">
            <h3 class="text-white font-semibold mb-1">RuntimeCollector</h3>
            <p class="text-sm text-gray-400">JVM heap, thread count, GC stats.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="p-4 rounded-xl border border-white/10 bg-white/[0.02]">
            <h3 class="text-white font-semibold mb-1">KontainerCollector</h3>
            <p class="text-sm text-gray-400">Services created, injection times.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="p-4 rounded-xl border border-white/10 bg-white/[0.02]">
            <h3 class="text-white font-semibold mb-1">UserCollector</h3>
            <p class="text-sm text-gray-400">Authenticated user info for the request.</p>
        </div>
    </div>

    <h2>Insights GUI</h2>

    <p>The module includes a web-based debug toolbar, mounted at <code>/_/insights/</code>.
        Browse recent requests, inspect database queries, view timing breakdowns, and check container usage &mdash;
        all without external tools.</p>

    <Aside>Insights is the reason Kontainer has per-request scoping.
        Each collector is a dynamic service that accumulates data throughout one request,
        then gets serialized and stored.
    </Aside>

    <div class="mt-12">
        <a href="/ultra/funktor/logging"
           class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 px-6 py-3 rounded-lg bg-brand-400/10 text-brand-400 border border-brand-400/30 hover:bg-brand-400/20 transition-all font-medium">
            Logging Module &rarr;
        </a>
    </div>

</DocsLayout>
